bilingual.source: What is the importance of trees in the water cycle?
bilingual.target: 树木在水循环中有何重要性？

bilingual.source: Explain why the water cycle is called 'everlasting'.
bilingual.target: 解释为什么水循环被称为“永恒”。

bilingual.source: We forget that the water cycle and the life cycle are one.
bilingual.target: 我们忘记了水循环和生命循环是一体的。

bilingual.source: Condensation is a key part of the water cycle.
bilingual.target: 凝结是水循环的关键部分。

bilingual.source: Plants cycle nutrients through their roots and leaves.
bilingual.target: 植物通过根和叶循环养分。

bilingual.source: Evaporation is a key process in the water cycle.
bilingual.target: 蒸发是水循环中的一个关键过程。

bilingual.source: Their actions are perpetuating a cycle of violence.
bilingual.target: 他们的行为在使暴力循环持续。

bilingual.source: The water cycle is essential for life on Earth.
bilingual.target: 水的循环对地球上的生命至关重要。

bilingual.source: The water cycle is crucial for maintaining ecosystems.
bilingual.target: 水循环对维持生态系统非常重要。

bilingual.source: The moon goes through a cycle of phases every month.
bilingual.target: 月亮每个月都会经历一个相位循环。

list.abstract: cycle（[ˈsaɪkl]），英语单词。作名词时，释义为循环；整套；自行车。作动词时，释义为骑自行车；循环。例句：The cycle of renewal never ends.（更新的循环永无止境）。 作名词时，近义词为circle、revolution、rotation。作及物动词时，近义词为circulate。作不及物动词时，近义词为circumrotate、ride a bike。

yingyinNormal.en: In China, the New Year can start from like, the middle of January than to the end of February. And this lunar cycle repeats itself every 12 years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中国的春节那天会在是1月中旬到2月底其间的一天。这种农历的循环每12年重复一次。

yingyinNormal.en: We all know that we are better than the cynicism and the pessimism that is regurgitated throughout Washington, and the 24-hour cable news cycle, not my channel by the way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们知道，我们要好过华盛顿政府以及24小时循环播放的有线新闻中的犬儒主义与厌世主义，还好不是我的频道。

yingyinNormal.en: Before you go, consider this. Not only do I have a deep cycle marine battery power source which is more than capable of running our entertainment system, I also have all 61 episodes of the BBC series Red Dwarf and Fiddle Faddle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，考虑下这个，我不但有深循环的海军陆战队电池，这能更好地支持我们的娱乐活动。我还有一共61集的BBC科幻剧《红矮星号》，还有《无聊星人》。

yingyinNormal.en: She said that if you want to break the bad boyfriend cycle, you can do like a cleansing ritual.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她说想要停止与恶男交往的恶性循环，可以举行一个清理仪式。

yingyinNormal.en: Some regulate the cell cycle more effectively than others.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们中的某些在调节细胞周期上比其他要更高效。

yingyinNormal.en: The Cycle ride.
yingyinNormal.zh: 骑自行车。

yingyinNormal.en: Today is a good day for a cycle ride. A cycle ride, yippee. Peppa and George love cycle ride.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天是个骑自行车的好日子。骑自行车，太好了！佩奇和乔治喜欢骑自行车。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you thinking Senate next cycle? No, I'm thinking your district, this cycle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在考虑下一轮竞选参议员吗？不，我在考虑本轮竞选你的选区。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, if you assume 15 tampons per cycle and a 28-day cycle. Are you fairly regular?
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在假设你每次用15条，28天一周期，你经期正常吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Normally, cell division follows an orderly process called the cell cycle, which is basically the life cycle of a cell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一般来说，细胞分裂遵循一个叫做“细胞周期”的有序的进程，也就是一个细胞的生命周期。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm already on one painful cycle. I don't want to get on another one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经有一个痛苦的经期[自行车]了，我不想再多要一个。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, I'm not ready to have a baby. Oh, yes, you are! I track your cycle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，我还没准备好要孩子。你准备好了！我算着你的生理周期呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Aha. This looks like fun. I'll be able to cycle and watch TV at the same time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 啊哈.这看起来很好玩.我可以一边骑自行车一边看电视。

yingyinNormal.en: Aha. This looks like fun. I'll be able to cycle and watch TV at the same time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 啊哈.这看起来很好玩.我可以一边骑自行车一边看电视。

yingyinNormal.en: Step 1: Find the next date of Chinese New Year, which changes with the lunar cycle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一步：找到中国新年之后的一天，这是随着阴历周期的变化而变化的。

yingyinNormal.en: Forgive me if I'm not sympathetic to the fluctuations of your sleep cycle, Mr. Lowe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉，我没法同情你那不稳定的睡眠状况，罗威先生。

yingyinNormal.en: There's nothing left to map. I've run every inch of it myself. Every cycle. Every pattern.
yingyinNormal.zh: 全部都在这里了，我跑遍了迷宫的每个角落，每一层，每面墙。

yingyinNormal.en: Never mind. I clearly woke you up in the middle of a rem cycle. You're in no state of mind to talk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没事儿，很明显我在你熟睡的时候叫醒了你，你根本就没心情听我说话。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, don't worry. I'll use the gentle cycle. Okay. Basically, you wanna use one machine for all your whites. Okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 别担心，我会用轻柔绞洗。好的，你得用一台洗你全部的白衣白衣。

yingyinNormal.en: This redundancy is a good thing because you only need one functioning BRCA1 gene in a cell to regulate the cell cycle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这种“多余”其实是件好事，因为你虽然只需要一个乳腺癌1号基因工作就能控制细胞周期。

examination_example.sentence: Called conditional cash transfers or CCTs, these social assistance programs are designed to reduce inequality and break the <highlight>cycle</highlight> of poverty.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些被称为“有条件现金转移”的社会援助项目旨在减少不平等，打破贫困循环。

examination_example.sentence: It would be a mistake to think we are right now simply experiencing the painful side of a boom and bust <highlight>cycle</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 认为我们现在只是在经历繁荣和萧条周期的痛苦一面，那是错的。

examination_example.sentence: These brands have hijacked fashion <highlight>cycles</highlight>, shaking an industry long accustomed to a seasonal pace.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些品牌劫持了时尚周期，动摇了该行业长久以来流行周期随季节而变化的节奏。

word_usage.usage: cycle和circle都表示“圈”，但cycle更多是抽象的圈，表示“循环、周期”等；而circle更多是实体的圈，表示“圆圈、环状物、线圈”等。

examination_example.sentence: CEO Chris Cocalis of Pivot <highlight>Cycles</highlight>, which sells high-end mountain bikes, found that U. S. bike shops weren't interested in stocking ebikes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 销售高端山地车的皮沃自行车首席执行官克里斯·科卡利斯发现，美国自行车商店对储存息税前利润不感兴趣。

examination_example.sentence: Ebike riders get the enjoyable part of <highlight>cycling</highlight> without the massive suffering of climbing huge hills.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电动自行车的骑手可以享受骑车的乐趣，而且不用忍受爬山的巨大痛苦。

examination_example.sentence: Within weeks, her depression had begun to ease as she <highlight>cycled</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几周之内，她的抑郁症随着骑自行车(这种运动)开始缓解。

examination_example.sentence: What we do know is that people tend to have different kinds of nightmares at different points during the sleep <highlight>cycle</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们所知道的是，人们往往会在睡眠周期的不同时刻做不同类型的噩梦。

examination_example.sentence: Their daily routine followed the rhythm of the natural <highlight>cycle</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们的日常生活遵循自然循环的规律。

examination_example.sentence: This comfortable <highlight>cycle</highlight>, in which the rhythms of the day helped shape the rhythms of the meals, gave rise to large midday meal.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在这种舒适的循环中，一天的节奏有助于形成用餐的节奏，这就产生了一顿丰盛的午餐。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 打破“我累了”、“太难了”或“太远了”的怪圈。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>cycle</highlight> begins again until there are no more ball in the top of the clock.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个循环又开始了，直到时钟顶端不再有球为止。

examination_example.sentence: Plants are also part of the water <highlight>cycle</highlight> (水循环).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 植物也是水循环的一部分。

examination_example.sentence: If you can, try <highlight>cycling</highlight>, walking, or using public transport to get out and about, instead of using the car.
